<h1>Problem 2000 - 2023 IMOSL, A5</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 8</h2>
<p>Let \(a_1,a_2,\dots,a_{2023}\) be positive integers such that \(a_1,a_2,\dots,a_{2023}\) is a permutation of \(1,2,\dots,2023\), and \(|a_1-a_2|,|a_2-a_3|,\dots,|a_{2022}-a_{2023}|\) is a permutation of \(1,2,\dots,2022\). Prove that \(\max(a_1,a_{2023})\ge 507\).</p>
